org.dudss.nodeshot.misc

Interface PathHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefinitePathHandler, IndefinitePathHandler

    public interface PathHandler
    A handler assigned to each movable Package that handles actions after its assigned package has finished its current connector line segment. Most importantly this handler represents the path-finding logic of the Package.
